The European Union (EU) is often criticized for a heavy regulatory touch. What is the reality? This automatically updated research document gives a real-time overview of the EUâs legislative output.

Up to 19 May, 2022, the EU and its predecessors have produced 139706 number of regulations, 4255 number of directives, 35697 number of decisions and 1296 number of recommendations, according to Eur-Lex data pulled via the eurlex package for R and a SPARQL API maintained by the Publications Office of the European Union.
